  "keyFeatures": [
    "Custom and remote LLM evaluators with flexible return types",
    "Structured experimentation framework for systematic LLM testing",
    "OpenTelemetry-based distributed tracing with @traced decorator and start_span context manager",
    "Prompt management with versioning, labels, and multiple template engines",
    "Integrations with OpenAI, Anthropic, and other LLM providers via OpenInference",
    "Async support throughout the SDK (AsyncRemoteEvaluator, AsyncStructuredEvaluator)",
    "Configurable via code, environment variables, or YAML config file"
  ],
